Africa’s SADC, EAC, COMESA Blocs Plan to Merge, South Africa’s Davies Says

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-06-06T08:33:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/africa-s-sadc-eac-comesa-blocs-plan-to-merge-south-africa-s-davies-says.html
The  Southern African Development
Community , the  East African Community  and the Common Market for
Eastern and Southern Africa trade blocs plan to merge, Rob
Davies, the country’s trade minister, told reporters in
Johannesburg today.  South Africa  will host trade talks next week, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
